snippet.title: BeeBeeQ Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
BeeBeeQ is an Asymmetrical VR Party game.

Take flight with your friends as a squadron of bees, protect your home from the gargantuan chef!

Or

Take on the role of the Chef, it’s not going to be easy, all you want is a quiet Sunday afternoon, but these pesky bees are relentless.

 http://popupasylum.co.uk/beebeeq
